The evidence with the title 'Genetic evolution: how the Ebola virus changes and adapts ' says Sep 16, 2014  ... Like all viruses , the Ebola virus has evolved since the outbreak  ... This natural change of virus genomes over time is why influenza virus vaccines must be updated annually and why HIV mutates to become resistant to antiretroviral drugs .  ... Or changes within the virus which may make the new host sicker . 
